{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":null,"text":"左右翼先行！","tone":"厉声","chapter":216,"line_start":23,"line_end":23},{"speaker":"char_zhai_jiao","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":null,"text":"追！","tone":"厉声","chapter":216,"line_start":45,"line_end":45},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"不要追！","tone":"厉声","chapter":216,"line_start":47,"line_end":47},{"speaker":"char_zhai_jiao","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"为何不追，李密要走哩！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":216,"line_start":49,"line_end":49},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_ling_long_jiao","text":"尘土扬起的样子算是条条而起还是凌星散乱呢？","tone":"疑问","chapter":216,"line_start":53,"line_end":55},{"speaker":"char_ling_long_jiao","speaker_name":"玲珑娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"瓦岗敌军仍是队形整肃，散而不乱。","tone":"陈述","chapter":216,"line_start":57,"line_end":59},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"正如我所料，沈落雁早猜到有伏兵，故以怪鸟叫我们追去，我敢肯定密林内另有伏兵，当我们步入陷阱时，李密就会回师反击。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":61,"line_end":63},{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":null,"text":"有道理！","tone":"激动","chapter":216,"line_start":65,"line_end":65},{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"现在该如何处置？","tone":"疑问","chapter":216,"line_start":79,"line_end":79},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_yang_gong_qing","text":"我们只须留下数千人在这里布防，教李密难作寸进。而辎重则继续渡河，并分出快速部队直逼洛口，攻他一个措手不及。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":81,"line_end":85},{"speaker":"char_xuan_yong","speaker_name":"宣永","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"如若李密回师守洛口，我们是否仍要强攻？","tone":"疑问","chapter":216,"line_start":87,"line_end":87},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_xuan_yong","text":"李密是不会甘心退走的，他还有单雄信这个希望，到单雄信乘我们进军洛口撤走时，他便错恨难返，只有逃往虎牢一途了。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":89,"line_end":91},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":null,"text":"快速部队的作用，就是先一步赶往洛口，防止李密渡河回城，那洛口的邴元真便只有弃城或投降的两个选择。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":97,"line_end":99},{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":null,"text":"就这么决定吧！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":216,"line_start":101,"line_end":101}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_kou_zhong","name":"寇仲","alias":[],"identity":"双龙帮首领，谋略出众的统帅","faction":"双龙帮","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"本章展现其从战场新手蜕变为料敌如神的统帅","personality":{"traits":["果敢","冷静","重情义","有谋略","豪迈","深谋远虑"],"speech_style":"豪爽直接，战场上方显沉稳","temperament":"热血果敢"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xu_zi_ling","type":"挚友","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"并肩作战的兄弟"},{"target":"char_zhai_jiao","type":"合作者","intensity":60,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"军事同盟"},{"target":"char_yang_gong_qing","type":"合作者","intensity":70,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"互相欣赏的战友"},{"target":"char_chu_chu","type":"恋人","intensity":75,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"情深难舍"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[216],"source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":3,"line_end":3,"text":"寇仲惊呼"}]},{"id":"char_xu_zi_ling","name":"徐子陵","alias":[],"identity":"寇仲挚友，冷静观察者","faction":"双龙帮","role":"protagonist","archetype":"scholar","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"冷静观察寇仲的成长，感叹人生如梦","personality":{"traits":["冷静","深沉","淡泊","智慧","重情义"],"speech_style":"淡然深沉","temperament":"淡泊宁静"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"挚友","intensity":95,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"并肩作战的兄弟"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[216],"source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":71,"line_end":71,"text":"徐子陵留意寇仲"}]},{"id":"char_yang_gong_qing","name":"杨公卿","alias":[],"identity":"王世充麾下大将军","faction":"王世充军","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"出神入化","one_line":"欣赏寇仲的军事才能，为其提供便利离开","personality":{"traits":["豪爽","识才","重义","果断","老练"],"speech_style":"豪迈大笑，将军气度","temperament":"豪爽"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","in