到多个城池"}]},{"id":"faction_shuang_long_bang","name":"双龙帮","type":"帮派","location":"关中","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"寇仲与徐子陵创立的帮派","source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":235,"line_end":235,"text":"双龙帮的人在关中苦候他的来临"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_luo_kou","name":"洛口","region":"河南","one_line":"李密重要据点，邴元真镇守","source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":97,"line_end":99,"text":"快速部队直逼洛口"}]},{"id":"loc_hu_lao","name":"虎牢","region":"河南","one_line":"李密逃往的据点","source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":107,"line_end":107,"text":"李密知道大势已去，只得率人逃往虎牢"}]},{"id":"loc_luo_yang","name":"洛阳","region":"河南","one_line":"东都洛阳，王世充势力中心","source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":273,"line_end":273,"text":"东都洛阳出现前方"}]}],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_tu_shu_fang","speaker_name":"屠叔方","listener":null,"text":"我已向小姐和盘托出有关南方的形势和素素的事情，因我觉得还是坦白些好。","tone":"陈述","chapter":216,"line_start":121,"line_end":123},{"speaker":"char_zhai_jiao","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"这么要紧的事竟敢瞒我，看我把你们和那香玉山一起宰掉。","tone":"愤怒","chapter":216,"line_start":125,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_zhai_jiao","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":null,"text":"我岂是不讲道理的人，李密今次已吃足苦头，永无翻身之望。虽未能手刃那奸贼，总算为爹重出了一口气。我也不想为王世充这种人继续出力，你们有甚么打算？","tone":"陈述","chapter":216,"line_start":131,"line_end":135},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_zhai_jiao","text":"我们想先回洛阳打个转，然后立即南下，先助飞马牧场反危为安，再看怎样可把素姐母子带走，再来与小姐会合。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":137,"line_end":137},{"speaker":"char_zhai_jiao","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":null,"text":"我和你们一道去吧！","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":141,"line_end":141},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_zhai_jiao","text":"小姐千万不要去。","tone":"焦急","chapter":216,"line_start":143,"line_end":143},{"speaker":"char_zhai_jiao","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"为甚么？","tone":"愤怒","chapter":216,"line_start":145,"line_end":145},{"speaker":"char_tu_shu_fang","speaker_name":"屠叔方","listener":"char_zhai_jiao","text":"小仲的意思，是希望小姐能留在北方，为他联结瓦岗军有用的人才，好得在将来共创大业。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":147,"line_end":149},{"speaker":"char_xu_zi_ling","speaker_name":"徐子陵","listener":"char_zhai_jiao","text":"小姐留在北方，看紧李密，便随时可取他狗命。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":151,"line_end":151},{"speaker":"char_zhai_jiao","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":null,"text":"好吧！我便留在北方，不过我再不想跟王世充的人混在一起。你们想甚么时候走？","tone":"无奈","chapter":216,"line_start":155,"line_end":157},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"翟娇","listener":null,"text":"事不宜迟，明早我们便一起离开。","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":159,"line_end":159},{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"仲小兄想就此一走了事吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":216,"line_start":161,"line_end":163},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_yang_gong_qing","text":"大将军真精明。","tone":"苦笑","chapter":216,"line_start":165,"line_end":165},{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"你是杨某人生平所遇的最天才横溢的统帅人才，假以时日经验，天下再难有对手，你心中有没有甚么计划呢？","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":167,"line_end":169},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_yang_gong_qing","text":"暂时可以有甚么计划呢？只不过觉得王公非是可与共事之辈，故暂作功成身退，大家仍可留下一份交情。","tone":"无奈","chapter":216,"line_start":171,"line_end":173},{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"我明白你的感受，论功行赏，怎能没你的份儿？明天我便派战船把你送返洛阳，理由则是让你可亲自向大人汇报军情，以决定是否该立即渡大河进攻河阳。但你既萌去志，洛阳再不是该久留之地，你明白我的话吧？","tone":"认真","chapter":216,"line_start":175,"line_end":181},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_yang_gong_qing","text":"我绝不会忘记和大将军并肩作战的美好时光。","tone":"激动","chapter":216,"line_start":183,"line_end":183},{"speaker":"char_yang_gong_qing","speaker_name":"杨公卿","listener":null,"text":"彼此彼此！希望有机会再并骑驰骋沙场，杀敌取胜。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":216,"line_start":185,"line_end":187},{"speaker":"char_chu_chu","speaker_name":"楚楚","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"寇爷！","tone":"柔声","chapter":216,"line_start":189,"line_end":189},{"speaker":"char_chu_chu","speaker_name":"楚楚","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"听小姐说明天便要和你们分手了！是吗？","tone":"悲伤","chapter":216,"line_start":193,"line_end":195},{"speaker":"char_kou_zhong","speaker_name":"寇仲","listener":"char_chu_chu","text":"南方事了，我定会回来找你，你还可以见到素姐和她那白胖胖的婴孩啊！","tone":"温柔","chapter":216,"line_start":197,"line_end":199},{"speaker":"char_chu_chu","speaker_name":"楚楚","listener":"char_kou_zhong","text":"那真是好哩！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":216,"line_start":201,"line_end":201}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_tu_shu_fang","name":"屠叔方","alias":[],"identity":"瓦岗军旧部，翟娇信任之人","faction":"瓦岗军","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"向翟娇坦白南方形势和素素之事","personality":{"traits":["坦诚","忠诚","稳重","有担当","重义"],"speech_style":"沉稳直接","temperament":"稳重"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_zhai_jiao","type":"合作者","intensity":65,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"旧部与主公之女"},{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"合作者","intensity":55,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"军事同盟"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[216],"source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":121,"line_end":121,"text":"屠叔方引来翟娇"}]},{"id":"char_chu_chu","name":"楚楚","alias":["俏婢"],"identity":"翟娇的俏婢，寇仲情人","faction":"双龙帮","role":"companion","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"对寇仲情深难舍的俏婢","personality":{"traits":["温柔","深情","忠诚","脆弱","善解人意"],"speech_style":"柔声细语，幽幽深情","temperament":"温柔"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"恋人","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"情深难舍"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[216],"source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":191,"line_end":191,"text":"原来是动人的俏婢楚楚"}]},{"id":"char_su_su","name":"素素","alias":["素姐"],"identity":"寇仲的义姐，身在南方","faction":"双龙帮","role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"身在南方，急待寇仲营救","personality":{"traits":["善良","柔弱","慈爱","坚韧","无私"],"speech_style":"不详","temperament":"温柔"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_kou_zhong","type":"亲属","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"义姐弟"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[216],"source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":239,"line_end":239,"text":"素素则急待他去营救"}]},{"id":"char_bing_yuan_zhen","name":"邴元真","alias":[],"identity":"镇守洛口的李密部将","faction":"瓦岗军","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"登堂入室","one_line":"向杨公卿投降的洛口守将","personality":{"traits":["识时务","谨慎","务实","有自知之明","果断"],"speech_style":"不详","temperament":"务实"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[216],"source_refs":[{"chapter":216,"line_start":105,"line_end":105,"text":"镇守洛口的邴元真向兵临城下的杨公卿投降"}]},{"id":"char_wang_bo_dang","name":"王伯当","alias":[],"identity":"李密部将，退守河阳","faction":"瓦岗军","role":"npc","